ый no-fee acceptance flow для моряков до следующих этапов identity и workspace integration."],"\n            "],"\n          "],"\n          ",["LI",{},"\n            ",["A",{"href":"https://crewportglobal.com/legal/no-recruitment-fees/"},"\n              ",["SPAN",{"class":"doc-type","data-i18n":"home.docNoFeesType"},"Политика"],"\n              ",["STRONG",{"class":"doc-title","data-i18n":"home.docNoFeesTitle"},"Политика отсутствия рекрутинговых сборов"],"\n              ",["SPAN",{"class":"doc-note","data-i18n":"home.docNoFeesBody"},"Ключевой публичный trust document для моряков и судовладельцев."],"\n            "],"\n          "],"\n          ",["LI",{},"\n            ",["A",{"href":"https://crewportglobal.com/about/"},"\n              ",["SPAN",{"class":"doc-type","data-i18n":"home.docScopeType"},"Позиционирование"],"\n              ",["STRONG",{"class":"doc-title","data-i18n":"home.docScopeTitle"},"Границы проекта и позиционирование"],"\n              ",["SPAN",{"class":"doc-note","data-i18n":"home.docScopeBody"},"Определяет, чем платформа является и чем не является на Stage 1."],"\n            "],"\n          "],"\n          ",["LI",{},"\n            ",["A",{"href":"https://crewportglobal.com/how-it-works/"},"\n              ",["SPAN",{"class":"doc-type","data-i18n":"home.docHowType"},"Обзор"],"\n              ",["STRONG",{"class":"doc-title","data-i18n":"home.docHowTitle"},"Как это работает"],"\n              ",["SPAN",{"class":"doc-note","data-i18n":"home.docHowBody"},"Объясняет начальный workflow для судовладельцев и моряков."],"\n            "],"\n          "],"\n           ",["LI",{},"\n            ",["A",{"href":"https://crewportglobal.com/legal/privacy/"},"\n               ",["SPAN",{"class":"doc-type","data-i18n":"home.docPrivacyType"},"Юридическое"],"\n               ",["STRONG",{"class":"doc-title","data-i18n":"home.docPrivacyTitle"},"Политика конфиденциальности"],"\n               ",["SPAN",{"class":"doc-note","data-i18n":"home.docPrivacyBody"},"П